        //- Modal for image preview of FivePD Mod
        .modal.fade.bd-example-modal-lg(id="gtaModModal" tabindex="-1")
            .modal-dialog.modal-lg.modal-dialog-centered
                .modal-content
                    .modal-header
                        h5.modal-title Grand Theft Auto V Mod
                        button(type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal")
                            span &times;
                    .modal-body
                        .container
                            .row.flex-wrap
                                p.d-inline.bg-secondary.rounded.text-white.p-1.mr-2 C#
                                p.d-inline.bg-secondary.rounded.text-white.p-1.mr-2 Object Oriented
                                p.d-inline.bg-secondary.rounded.text-white.p-1.mr-2 FivePD API
                                p.d-inline.bg-secondary.rounded.text-white.p-1.mr-2 Git
                            .row.mt-1.summary
                                p This project came to be when a couple of my friends were always seen playing together on thier own modded Grand Theft Auto V server. 
                                    | When I asked them what was so fun about it, they told me its because it was a roleplay server to play as cops and robbers. This led 
                                    | me to hop on and play too! Then I realized the developers also created an API so that others can join and create mods as well. 
                                    | Thus, I created a mod that I uploaded on thier community website for others to enjoy as my friends did on thier server. The mod now has 
                                    | over 1,100 downloads and couldnt have been done without the help of the FivePD community.
                    .modal-footer
                        a.btn.btn-outline-dark(href="https://gtapolicemods.com/index.php?/files/file/1171-suspicious-person-callout-multiple-outcomes/" target="_blank" role="button") Website
